<!--
  Simula Ad SDK - SKAdNetwork Configuration
  Required for iOS ad attribution (iOS 14+)

  INSTALLATION:
  1. Open your app's Info.plist in Xcode
  2. Add a new key: SKAdNetworkItems (Array)
  3. Copy the SKAdNetworkIdentifier entries below into your Info.plist

  Or merge this entire array into your existing SKAdNetworkItems if you have other ad SDKs.

  For more info: https://developer.apple.com/documentation/storekit/skadnetwork
-->
